Warmed Foccacia Slices: Cut 1 loaf Safeway SELECT Artisan Onion, Italian, or Jalapeno Cheese Foccacia (12 oz.) into 6 equal pieces or wedges. Set pieces in a 10- by 15-inch baking pan; bake in a 350 degree oven until bread is warm, about 10 minutes. Avocado Cream: Peel and pit 1 firm-ripe avocado (6 oz.). Cut avocado into chunks and place in a blender. Add 2 tablespoons chopped green onion (including green tops), 2 tablespoons chopped fresh cilantro, and 2 teaspoons lime juice. Whirl until smoothly blended. Scoop mixture into a bowl and add salt to taste.